                  <Text layoutX="52.0" layoutY="774.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="There are many programming languages, each suited for different tasks. Popular languages include Python, Java, C++, and JavaScript. Choosing the right language depends on your project goals. Alongside programming languages, developers use Integrated Development Environments (IDEs) like Visual Studio Code, Eclipse, or NetBeans. These tools provide features like syntax highlighting, code suggestions, and debugging tools, making coding more efficient and error-free." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
